column16: Troy Glaus strikes out swinging and Ryan Ludwick caught stealing 2nd, catcher Paul Bako to second baseman Jerry Hairston.
Albert Pujols homers (37) on a line drive to left field.
Felipe Lopez strikes out on foul tip.
Hunter Pence pops out to second baseman Danny Richar.
Geoff Blum singles on a fly ball to center fielder Corey Patterson.
Lance Berkman flies out to left fielder Jerry Hairston.
Miguel Tejada singles on a fly ball to right fielder Jay Bruce.  Miguel Tejada out at 2nd, right fielder Jay Bruce to shortstop Jeff Keppinger.
Mike Rivera lines out to right fielder Jay Bruce.
Corey Hart grounds into double play, third baseman Adam Rosales to second baseman Wilkin Castillo to first baseman Joey Votto.    J.   Hardy out at 2nd.
J.   Hardy singles on a ground ball to third baseman Adam Rosales.
Mike Cameron flies out to center fielder Corey Patterson.
Jon Adkins intentionally walks Corey Hart.
